Current behavior: `ParameterResolutionException`is thrown, e.g. `ParameterResolver [ParameterResolverReproducerTest$IntegerResolver] resolved a value of type [java.lang.Integer] for parameter [long arg0] in executable [void ParameterResolverReproducerTest.failing(long)], but a value assignment compatible with [long] is required`.

Desired behavior, e.g. a `long` parameter can be called with an `Integer` argument

