## Description

There seems to be a potential race condition in [`NodeTestTask`](https://github.com/junit-team/junit-framework/blob/main/junit-platform-engine/src/main/java/org/junit/platform/engine/support/hierarchical/NodeTestTask.java). The issue appears to be related to concurrent access to the [`parentContext`](https://github.com/junit-team/junit-framework/blob/4d034a78bb64f870c1236457c3a50b79155da00b/junit-platform-engine/src/main/java/org/junit/platform/engine/support/hierarchical/NodeTestTask.java#L59) field.

The race condition appears to be present in the latest release too.

